# DOCS_TEST: example_001

query
select cast('1.1232154' as decimal(38, 7)) + cast('1' as decimal(10, 0));
----
?column?
2.1232154

query error
select cast('9999999999999999999999999999999.2345678' as decimal(38, 7)) + cast('1' as decimal(10, 0));
----
db error: ERROR: Overflow in addition of DECIMAL\(38\) \(99999999999999999999999999999992345678 \+ 10000000\);


